    "body": "Yeah it's probably going to take a while before a fully-fledged release.\r\n\r\nFWIW, I discovered in the meantime that you can use yarn v2 with node_modules instead of plug-n-play, with this magic [node_modules linker](https://yarnpkg.com/advanced/migration#if-required-enable-the-node-modules-plugin). If you do this, you inadvertently discard the zero-install approach, so you also have to modify your `.gitignore` file, as per the [instructions](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/60184159/yarn-v2-gitignore) here.",
